<title>Himak a̱ sai on okhlilit taiyaha ƲIT98</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Himak a̱ sai on okhlilit taiyaha,
 Nana moyuma kʋt chullosa hoka,
 Sa chu̱kʋsh ʋt nukha̱klo bieka hosh
 Lummʋt Klaist a̱ i̱ hʋchukbihlepa lishke.

[V2]
 Ʋb' A̱ki ʋt sa pesʋt, a̱ nukha̱klot,
 Nana ai ashahanchi li puta ka
 A mominchit a̱ kashoffa he mak o̱,
 Im asilhha li mak osh hlipia lishke.

[V3]
 Na̱ Nuktalali chi holitopa ma!
 Sa shilombish ʋno ithaiyana cha,
 Nuktalalit, yukpanlit ik i̱ hulló,
 Aiahni biekʋt chim asilhha lishke.

[V4]
 Chisʋs ma! Na̱ pi Okchalinchi chia,
 Chiso ashʋchi, chiso nukha̱klo ya̱
 Auet anukfillit et okchalinchi̱;
 Chi ai okcha̱ya bʋnnʋt chim ilbʋsha li.</lyrics>
<aka>Evening Hymn</aka>
<author>Cyrus Byington, Tune: &quot;Morning Star of the Spirit.&quot;</author>
<hymn_number>98</hymn_number>
</song>